---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`${SITE_TITLE} - 泰國暗黑行程指南 | 曼谷夜生活評測、地圖、避坑`} description="ThaiNights.net 是最專業的泰國夜生活指南。提供曼谷 Nana Plaza, Soi Cowboy 等紅燈區深度評測、互動地圖、泰國按摩避坑攻略，支援繁體與簡體中文。" />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 1000px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 1rem;
				color: #e0e0e0;
			}
			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			.hero h1 {
				font-size: 3.5rem;
				color: var(--neon-blue);
				text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-blue);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			.hero p {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				color: var(--gray);
			}
			.card-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
				gap: 2rem;
			}
			.card {
				background: #16161a;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid #333;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
			}
			.card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-5px);
				border-color: var(--neon-pink);
				box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.2);
			}
			.card h3 {
				margin-top: 0;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
			}
			.card p {
				flex: 1;
				color: var(--gray);
				font-size: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			.btn {
				background: var(--neon-pink);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 6px;
				text-decoration: none;
				display: inline-block;
				font-weight: bold;
				margin-top: 1rem;
				transition: opacity 0.2s;
			}
			.btn:hover {
				opacity: 0.9;
			}
			.read-more {
				color: var(--neon-pink);
				font-weight: bold;
				text-decoration: none;
				align-self: flex-start;
			}
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.hero h1 {
					font-size: 2.2rem;
				}
				.hero p {
					font-size: 1rem;
				}
				main {
					padding: 2rem 1rem;
				}
				.card-grid {
					gap: 1.5rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body style="background-color: #0a0a0c;">
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero">
				<h1>🇹🇭 ThaiNights</h1>
				<p>{SITE_DESCRIPTION}</p>
				<a href="/map" class="btn">查看互動地圖</a>
			</div>
			
			<div class="card-grid">
				<div class="card">
					<h3>📍 Nana Plaza</h3>
					<p>全球最大成人遊樂場，三層樓精華攻略、店家推薦與防坑提醒。</p>
					<a href="/blog/nana-plaza" class="read-more">閱讀評測 →</a>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>📍 Soi Cowboy</h3>
					<p>最受歡迎的霓虹小巷，必去店家推薦，感受曼谷最經典的夜生活。</p>
					<a href="/blog/soi-cowboy" class="read-more">閱讀評測 →</a>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>📍 芭達雅步行街</h3>
					<p>全球老司機的終極朝聖地，Walking Street 實戰生存守則。</p>
					<a href="/blog/pattaya-walking-street" class="read-more">閱讀評測 →</a>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>💆 按摩全攻略</h3>
					<p>從正統泰式按摩、抓龍筋到肥皂按摩，完整分類與店家指南。</p>
					<a href="/blog/massage-guide" class="read-more">閱讀評測 →</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
